        <div class="w3-container w3-margin-left w3-margin-right">
            <p>The following are some frequently asked questions regarding Covid-19. Please select the drop-down items to view the relevant answer to the questions. If these FAQs do not answer your questions, we reccommend you consult the <a href="https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/" target="_blank">CDC website</a> or contact your primary healthcare provider.</p>
